libs.content: find_program(gunzipcommand gunzip doc "path to gunzip executable")

find_library(gmsh_library
  names
    gmsh libgmsh
  doc "gmsh library path")

find_program(qt_xmlpatterns_executable
    names xmlpatterns-qt5 xmlpatterns
    hints "${qt5_dir}/../../../bin"
          "${qt5_dir}/../../../libexec/qt5/bin"
    doc   "path to xmlpatterns")

deps.context:
find_package(
  package     "qt${paraview_qt_major_version}"
  components  widgets
  version     5.12
  forward_version_req minor)

libs.content:
find_library(pythonqt_library
  names pythonqt
  doc   "the pythonqt library")

find_library(pythonqt_qtall_library
  names pythonqt_qtall
  doc   "the pythonqt_qtall library")

find_library(gmsh_library
  names
    gmsh libgmsh
  path_suffixes
    gmsh)

find_library(3dxwaresdk_library
  names tdxnavlib 3dconnexionnavlib
  hints
    ${3dxwaresdk_root}
    env 3dxwaresdk_dir
    env 3dxwaresdk_root
  path_suffixes
    lib/x64
    lib/x86
    lib
    ""
  doc "path to the 3dxwaresdk library"
)

find_library(vrpn_quat_library
      names quat
      doc   "vrpn quat library")

find_library(pdal_plugin_e57_library
  names
    pdal_plugin_reader_e57 libpdal_plugin_reader_e57
  hints "${pdal_library_dirs}"
  doc "pdal plugin e57")

find_library(vapor_vdf_library
  names vdf
  doc   "ncar vapor data format library")

find_library(vapor_common_library
  names common
  hints ${_vapor_vdf_library_dir}
  doc   "ncar vapor common library")
